OL,3,CMother and daughter who died in crash
OL,4,Cpictured as family pay tribute
OL,6,FA mother and her seven-year-old
OL,7,Fdaughter from Portsmouth who died in a
OL,8,Fcollision on the A3 have been pictured
OL,9,Ffor the first time.
OL,11,FMary Michelle Devine, 43, (known as
OL,12,FMichelle) and her daughter Theia, died
OL,13,Fwhen their car, a red Ford Fiesta left
OL,14,Fthe southbound carriageway just after
OL,15,Fthe Hindhead Tunnel on Thursday. (19
OL,16,FFebruary)
OL,18,FBoth were pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
