OL,3,CMother and daughter who died in crash
OL,4,Cpictured as family pay tribute
OL,6,FTheir family has now paid the
OL,7,Ffollowing tribute to them: "Our family
OL,8,Fmourn the most beautiful two souls you
OL,9,Fcould ever meet.
OL,11,F"Our beautiful, beloved little Theia
OL,12,Fwho had so much confidence and life in
OL,13,Fher and our crazy Michelle who was
OL,14,Fvibrant and had a heart of gold.
OL,16,F"We truly love them and will miss them
OL,17,Feveryday.
OL,19,F"They both had so much personality and
OL,20,Fso many loved ones, our hearts are
OL,21,Fbroken."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
